Century Counselors are available to assist you search for housing as well as to offer you support in other areas of your life that may be affected by a housing crisis; call 651-779-3285 for assistance.
https://www.century.edu/support-services/student-wellness/personal-counseling

If you're still looking for more information, here's a good resource for help:
http://century.custhelp.com/app/answers/detail/a_id/596
